in the economy he praised the soviet unions peace policy but 
did not mention gorbachevs political and economic changes 
last april in remarks ending a twoday central committee 
session jakes said the leadership wanted to elevate younger 
comrades and thus create conditions for further successful 
fulfillment of party tasks 
he said it was an important requirement to ensure that 
qualified young people are more frequently proposed for key 
economic and other jobs 
colotka has been premier of slovakia since may 1969 and deputy 
federal premier since september 1969 strougal replaced oldrich 
cernik as federal premier in january 1970 
