the crisis is cementing lebanons de facto partition into 
sectarian cantons in the nations 13yearold civil war 
the christians new move suggested that sfeir may sound out 
moslem leaders and possibly syria and the united states on a 
compromise candidate 
syria the main power broker in lebanon backs lebanons moslems 
