over the presidential crisis and the civil war 
political decentralization or federalization will not 
bring an end to the state of war but will kindle an endless war on 
the borders of the cantons it will also lead to endless wars in 
the streets alleys hills villages and towns hoss declared 
rightwing christians favor a federal system they believe it 
will safeguard their western way of life from what they perceive as 
the threat of irans brand of islamic fundamentalism such 
fundamentalism is growing among the shiites here lebanons largest 
single sect 
