chains or frozenfood sections and momandpop grocery stores kept 
crates of live chickens out back 
at the small store tucked away in a polish and italian 
neighborhood customers who order a fryer broiler or roaster take 
home chicken so fresh it was squawking 15 minutes earlier 
the butcher who wields his knife with a surgeons pride also 
sells fresh rabbit quail pigeon duck geese and the bantam 
roosters favored in some italian kitchens for stews and sauces 
