mine isnt so sure 
savekin came to the mine near palatka 14 years ago and now earns 
a salary of 800 rubles 1200 a month four times more than the 
nationwide average for an industrial worker like others with jobs 
underground he works a sixhour shift gets 54 days of vacation a 
year and will be eligible to retire at age 50 
palatka where savekin and moskvin live is a town of 
